## Content Governance

### Pre-Publish Checklist

Before any page goes live:

- [ ] Content follows Content Specifications
- [ ] Primary keyword assigned per Keyword Strategy
- [ ] Metadata optimized (title, description)
- [ ] Schema markup implemented
- [ ] Internal links included
- [ ] Mobile rendering verified
- [ ] Hreflang correct
- [ ] Page indexed (no accidental noindex)

### Quality Assurance Process

1. **Content creation**: Follow specifications
2. **Keyword check**: Verify keyword placement and density
3. **Technical check**: Schema, metadata, hreflang
4. **Mobile preview**: Verify rendering
5. **Link validation**: Verify internal links work
6. **Approval**: Sign off before production deployment

### Post-Launch Monitoring

| Timeframe | Check |
|-----------|-------|
| Day 1 | Indexing requested, no 404s |
| Week 1 | Position tracking started |
| Week 2 | Initial position/CTR review |
| Month 1 | Performance vs. baseline |
| Month 3 | Full impact assessment |

